# 76. Récapitulatif attaques / solutions

## DoS

Solution : rate limiting, firewall, IPS, anti-DDoS.

## DDoS

Solution : scrubbing center, anti-DDoS cloud, anycast, ACL opérateur.

## TCP SYN Flooding

Solution : SYN cookies, firewall, IPS.

## MAC Flooding

Solution : Port Security.

## VLAN Hopping

Solution : désactiver DTP, native VLAN dédiée, ports access.

## DHCP Starvation

Solution : DHCP Snooping, Port Security.

## DHCP Spoofing

Solution : DHCP Snooping, ports Trusted/Untrusted.

## ARP Spoofing

Solution : DAI.

## IP Spoofing

Solution : IP Source Guard.

## Attaque STP

Solution : BPDU Guard, Root Guard.

## Ransomware

Solution : sauvegardes testées, EDR, patching, segmentation.

## Phishing

Solution : formation, MFA, SEG, vérification.

## Malware

Solution : antivirus, mises à jour, moindre privilège.

